registry/marketplace

trusted brand

D. Beli commercial rights / assets tertentu

Contohnya:

trademark

domains

website

hosted services

enterprise contracts

customer relationships

Jadi, walaupun repo itu MIT, masih ada banyak benda bernilai yang boleh dijual.

